Entries.default: "There's a strange energy in this wind. Could that portal lead to the Beyond?"
"Good. With any luck, that is the end of that thing."
"Captain, I hope you have no wish to follow that beast?"
"Well. Nice to see a problem resolve itself for a change."
"You see that? It was like something had ahold of its tail!"
"Now that be the best sort of suck!"
"Don't tell me we're goin' in after it."
"If it is all the same, I would prefer to wait on the ship."
"Did you see? The portal, it just- whoosh!"
